	<li>Explore Prospective Insights in ICT R&amp;D&nbsp;- <a href="https://ec.europa.eu/jrc/en/predict" target="_blank">PREDICT</a>&nbsp;</li>
	<li>Monitor for <a href="http://www.pocbigdata.eu/monitorICTonlinevacancies/general_info/" target="_blank">ICT online vacancies</a></li>
	<li>Review the&nbsp;Europe's Digital Progress Report for <a href="https://ec.europa.eu/digital-single-market/en/european-digital-progress-report" target="_blank">2017</a></li>
</ul>
</div></div><div class="context-nav context-nav content-meta dsm-team-source"><div  class="field field-name-dsm-update-date field--dsm-update-date"><div class="field__items"><div class="context-nav__items"><span class="context-nav__item">Last update: 14 January 2019</span></div></div></div><div  class="field field-name-hr-1 field--hr-1"><div class="field__items"><hr class="hr--fullwidth"></div></div><div  class="field field-name-dsm-team-responsible field--dsm-team-responsible"><div class="field__items"><span class="label-inline context-nav__label"><span class="icon icon--info"></span> Team responsible</span><div class="context-nav__items"><span class="context-nav__item"><a href="/digital-single-market/en/content/digital-economy-and-skills-unit-f4">Digital Economy and Skills (Unit F.4)</a></span></div></div></div></div><div class="group-related-content field-group-section_group"><h2><span>You may be interested in</span></h2><div  class="field field-name-ds-content-related-content field--ds-content-related-content"><div class="field__items"><section id="block-dsm-dsm-related-content" class="block block-dsm clearfix">

      
    <div class="block__content">
