        <div class="col-lg-9 ">
          <div  class="field field-name-title field--title"><div class="field__items"><h1>Data protection</h1></div></div><div  class="field field-name-field-core-introduction field--field-core-introduction"><div class="field__items"><p>Rules for the protection of personal data inside and outside the EU.</p></div></div>        </div>

