          <div class="row">
        <section class="section section--content-top col-md-12 ">
        
        
          <div class="section"><div class="section__group section--row-three section--navigation"><div class="section__item"><div class="listing listing--navigation">


  <a href="/info/law/law-topic/data-protection/data-protection-eu_en" class="listing__item-link" title="Data protection in the EU"><span class="sr-only">Data protection in the EU</span></a>

  <h2 class="listing__section-title">Data protection in the EU</h2>
  <p class="listing__description">The General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), the Data Protection Law Enforcement Directive and other rules concerning the protection of personal data</p>




</div>
</div><div class="section__item"><div class="listing listing--navigation">


  <a href="/info/law/law-topic/data-protection/international-dimension-data-protection_en" class="listing__item-link" title="International dimension of data protection"><span class="sr-only">International dimension of data protection</span></a>

  <h2 class="listing__section-title">International dimension of data protection</h2>

  <div class="listing__item"><a href="/info/law/law-topic/data-protection/international-dimension-data-protection/rules-international-transfers-personal-data_en" class="listing__title">Rules on international data transfers</a></div><div class="listing__item"><a href="/info/law/law-topic/data-protection/data-transfers-outside-eu/eu-us-data-transfers_en" class="listing__title">EU-US data transfers</a></div><div class="listing__item"><a href="/info/law/law-topic/data-protection/data-transfers-outside-eu/adequacy-protection-personal-data-non-eu-countries_en" class="listing__title">Adequacy decisions</a></div><div class="listing__item"><a href="/info/law/law-topic/data-protection/international-dimension-data-protection/binding-corporate-rules-bcr_en" class="listing__title">Binding Corporate Rules (BCR)</a></div><div class="listing__item"><a href="/info/law/law-topic/data-protection/data-transfers-outside-eu/model-contracts-transfer-personal-data-third-countries_en" class="listing__title">Standard Contractual Clauses (SCC)</a></div><div class="listing__item"><a href="/info/law/law-topic/data-protection/data-transfers-outside-eu/transfer-air-passenger-name-record-data-and-terrorist-finance-tracking-programme_en" class="listing__title">Transfer of air passenger name record data and terrorist finance tracking programme</a></div>


</div>
</div><div class="section__item"><div class="listing listing--navigation">


  <a href="/info/law/law-topic/data-protection/reform_en" class="listing__item-link" title="Reform"><span class="sr-only">Reform</span></a>

  <h2 class="listing__section-title">Reform</h2>

  <div class="listing__item"><a href="/info/law/law-topic/data-protection/reform/rights-citizens_en" class="listing__title">Rights for citizens</a></div><div class="listing__item"><a href="/info/law/law-topic/data-protection/reform/rules-business-and-organisations_en" class="listing__title">Rules for business and organisations</a></div><div class="listing__item"><a href="/info/law/law-topic/data-protection/reform/what-personal-data_en" class="listing__title">What is personal data?</a></div><div class="listing__item"><a href="/info/law/law-topic/data-protection/reform/what-does-general-data-protection-regulation-gdpr-govern_en" class="listing__title">What does the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) govern?</a></div><div class="listing__item"><a href="/info/law/law-topic/data-protection/reform/what-constitutes-data-processing_en" class="listing__title">What constitutes data processing?</a></div><div class="listing__item"><a href="/info/law/law-topic/data-protection/reform/what-are-data-protection-authorities-dpas_en" class="listing__title">What are Data Protection Authorities (DPAs)?</a></div>


